              div.color-name
                p #272A38
                p Primary
          div.quarter
            div.color.fourth
              div.color-name
                p #BBBDCF
                p Secondary

      section.font-info
        div.content-wrapper
          p As Zectr been operating their surveys in multiple countries and languages, when looking for a suitable font I had to take that fact into account. I was looking for fonts that would have support for multiple languages, multiple sripts and include many ligatures.
          p There are not that many free fonts checking all of those boxes. But Rubik is one of them.

